arful or anxious? Always = 1, often = 0.75, sometimes = 0.5, seldom = 0.25, rarely or never = 0</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="7244370E" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="002F665B" w:rsidRDefault="002F665B" w:rsidP="002F665B"><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="1"/><w:numId w:val="1"/></w:numPr></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>Do you feel the older you get, the more useless you are, and have trouble doing anything? Always = 1, often = 0.75, sometimes = 0.5, seldom = 0.25, rarely or never = 0</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="3E00F6EB" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="002F665B" w:rsidRDefault="002F665B" w:rsidP="002F665B"><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="1"/><w:numId w:val="1"/></w:numPr></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>Do you always look on the bright side of things? Always = 1, often = 0.75, sometimes = 0.5, seldom = 0.25, rarely or never = 0</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="460D5F53" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="002F665B" w:rsidRDefault="002F665B" w:rsidP="002F665B"><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="1"/><w:numId w:val="1"/></w:numPr></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>Can you make your own decisions concerning your personal affairs? Always = 1, often = 0.75, sometimes = 0.5, seldom = 0.25, rarely or never = 0</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="0A0ED7B6" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="002F665B" w:rsidRPr="005D36F9" w:rsidRDefault="002F665B" w:rsidP="002F665B"><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="1"/><w:numId w:val="1"/></w:numPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="005D36F9"><w:t>Have you fallen down in the last two years? YES [Score 1], NO [Score 0]</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="76760B73" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="002F665B" w:rsidRPr="005D36F9" w:rsidRDefault="002F665B" w:rsidP="002F665B"><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="ListParagraph"/><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="1"/><w:numId w:val="1"/></w:numPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="005D36F9"><w:t>How often do you have trouble falling asleep? MOST OF THE TIME [Score 1], SOMET